<emphasis id="FED5EAD9FFEDFFAEFF152FBFFF34F917" bold="true" box="[136,157,1706,1732]" pageId="4" pageNumber="251">5.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="0BA14D48FFEDFFAEFF342FBFFD01F916" authority="Bentham (1840: 295)" authorityName="Bentham" authorityPageNumber="295" authorityYear="1840" box="[169,680,1706,1733]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Comolia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="4" pageNumber="251" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="microphylla">
<emphasis id="FED5EAD9FFEDFFAEFF342FBFFE09F916" bold="true" box="[169,416,1706,1733]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="251">Comolia microphylla</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="A8304B3AFFEDFFAEFE312FBFFD01F916" author="Bentham, G." box="[428,680,1706,1733]" pageId="4" pageNumber="251" pagination="286 - 324" refId="ref8495" refString="Bentham, G. (1840) Contributions towards a Flora of South America. - Enumeration of plants collected by Mr Schomburgk in British Guiana. Hooker's Journal of Botany 2: 286 - 324." type="journal article" year="1840">Bentham (1840: 295)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. Type:—British Guiana [
<collectingCountry id="B4B6765BFFEDFFAEFC512FBFFBE5F916" box="[972,1100,1706,1733]" name="Guyana" pageId="4" pageNumber="251">GUYANA</collectingCountry>
]. 1837, 
<emphasis id="FED5EAD9FFEDFFAEFB312FBEFA02F917" box="[1196,1451,1706,1732]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="251">R.H. Schomburgk 106</emphasis>
(
<typeStatus id="131A8869FFEDFFAEFF0D2FDBFF50F93B" box="[144,249,1742,1768]" pageId="4" pageNumber="251">lectotype</typeStatus>
designated by 
<bibRefCitation id="A8304B3AFFEDFFAEFE3A2FDBFDF8F93B" author="Wurdack, J. J." box="[423,593,1742,1768]" pageId="4" pageNumber="251" pagination="82 - 89" refId="ref11350" refString="Wurdack, J. J. (1993) Comolia DC. In: Gorts-van Rijn, A. R. A. &amp; Jansen-Jacobs, M. J. (Eds.) The Flora of the Guianas: 99. Melastomataceae. Koeltz Scientific Books, Koenigstein, pp. 82 - 89." type="book chapter" year="1993">Wurdack 1993</bibRefCitation>
: K! [K000261631]; isolectotypes: negative of B at F! [F0 
<accessionNumber id="D3F2AB28FFEDFFAEFB7B2FDBFAC0F93A" box="[1254,1385,1742,1769]" httpUri="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/nucleotide/BN016841" pageId="4" pageNumber="251">BN016841</accessionNumber>
], BR! [BR0000008930996], E! [E00505209], F! [F0360435F], TCD! [TCD0005165]).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="84BB6540FFEDFFAEFF152E2FFF78F7DB" pageId="4" pageNumber="251" type="description">
<paragraph id="CC1E36CBFFEDFFAEFF152E2FFF78F7DB" blockId="4.[136,1451,1850,2056]" pageId="4" pageNumber="251">
<emphasis id="FED5EAD9FFEDFFAEFF152E2FFF58F887" bold="true" box="[136,241,1850,1876]" pageId="4" pageNumber="251">Notes:—</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="0BA14D48FFEDFFAEFF6D2E2FFE4DF887" authorityName="Bentham" authorityYear="1840" box="[240,484,1850,1876]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Comolia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="4" pageNumber="251" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="microphylla">
<emphasis id="FED5EAD9FFEDFFAEFF6D2E2FFE4DF887" box="[240,484,1850,1876]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="251">Comolia microphylla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was described from 
<emphasis id="FED5EAD9FFEDFFAEFD7A2E2EFC43F887" box="[743,1002,1850,1876]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="251">R.H. Schomburgk 106</emphasis>
, but without a duplicate indicated as type (
<bibRefCitation id="A8304B3AFFEDFFAEFF542E4BFEDFF8AB" author="Bentham, G." box="[201,374,1886,1912]" pageId="4" pageNumber="251" pagination="286 - 324" refId="ref8495" refString="Bentham, G. (1840) Contributions towards a Flora of South America. - Enumeration of plants collected by Mr Schomburgk in British Guiana. Hooker's Journal of Botany 2: 286 - 324." type="journal article" year="1840">Bentham 1840</bibRefCitation>
). 
<bibRefCitation id="A8304B3AFFEDFFAEFE162E4BFDECF8AB" author="Wurdack, J. J." box="[395,581,1886,1912]" pageId="4" pageNumber="251" pagination="82 - 89" refId="ref11350" refString="Wurdack, J. J. (1993) Comolia DC. In: Gorts-van Rijn, A. R. A. &amp; Jansen-Jacobs, M. J. (Eds.) The Flora of the Guianas: 99. Melastomataceae. Koeltz Scientific Books, Koenigstein, pp. 82 - 89." type="book chapter" year="1993">Wurdack (1993)</bibRefCitation>
indicated the specimen at K (K000261631, 
<figureCitation id="549A2A4EFFEDFFAEFBD82E4BFB0EF8AB" box="[1093,1191,1886,1912]" captionStart="FIGURE 4" captionStartId="6.[136,229,1953,1975]" captionTargetBox="[195,1406,191,1928]" captionTargetId="figure-23@6.[181,1406,190,1928]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="FIGURE 4. Photograph of the lectotype of Comolia microphylla Benth. at K. Source: ©Royal Botanic Gardens, Kew, K000261631. Available in: http://specimens.kew.org/herbarium/K000261631." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5423981" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5423981/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="251">Figure 4</figureCitation>
) as the 
<typeStatus id="131A8869FFEDFFAEFA982E4BFACEF8AB" box="[1285,1383,1886,1912]" pageId="4" pageNumber="251">holotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="0BA14D48FFEDFFAEFA0F2E4AFEA7F84F" authorityName="Bentham" authorityYear="1840" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Comolia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="4" pageNumber="251" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="microphylla">
<emphasis id="FED5EAD9FFEDFFAEFA0F2E4AFEA7F84F" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="251">C. microphylla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, which is an inadvertent lectotypification (see Article 7.11 of the ICN). This material at K was certainly analyzed by George Bentham (1800–1884), as suggested by the Herbarium Benthamianum stamp in this sheet (
<figureCitation id="549A2A4EFFEDFFAEFAFD2EB3FF31F837" captionStart="FIGURE 4" captionStartId="6.[136,229,1953,1975]" captionTargetBox="[195,1406,191,1928]" captionTargetId="figure-23@6.[181,1406,190,1928]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="FIGURE 4. Photograph of the lectotype of Comolia microphylla Benth. at K. Source: ©Royal Botanic Gardens, Kew, K000261631. Available in: http://specimens.kew.org/herbarium/K000261631." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5423981" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5423981/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="251">Figure 4</figureCitation>
), as Bentham identified and distributed the collections of the Schomburgk brothers (
<bibRefCitation id="A8304B3AFFEDFFAEFBD62EDFFF6DF7DB" author="Romero-Gonzalez, G. A. &amp; Campbell, L. M." pageId="4" pageNumber="251" pagination="295 - 307" refId="ref10499" refString="Romero-Gonzalez, G. A. &amp; Campbell, L. M. (2001) George Bentham's &quot; Enumeration of plants collected by Mr. Schomburgk, British Guiana &quot;. Harvard Papers in Botany 6: 295 - 307." type="journal article" year="2001">Romero-González &amp; Campbell 2001</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
